'''Xawaadle''' ({{lang-en|''Hawadle''}}; {{lang-ar|حوادله}}) waa [[Beelaha Soomaalida|beel]] ka mid ah [[Hawiye|Beelweynta Hawiye]] ee dadka [[Soomaali]]da, kuwaasi oo deegaan ku ah wadanka [[Soomaaliya]].<ref>{{cite book|title=Somalia at the Crossroads|year=2007|publisher=Adonis & Abbey|pages=10|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=CXUwAQAAIAAJ}}</ref>
==Hordhac==
Beesha Xawaadle waxay ka tirsan tahay beelweynta [[Irir Samaale]], ee laga helo deegaano badan oo ka tirsan [[Geeska Afrika]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Chapin Metz, ed.|first1=Helen|title=Somalia: A Country Study|url=http://countrystudies.us/somalia/66.htm|publisher=The Federal Research Division of the Library of Congress|accessdate=18 June 2016}}</ref> Intaas waxaa dheer, beesha Habargidir waxay si rasmi ah u degaan [[Soomaaliya|Gobolada Dhexe]] ee wadanka Soomaaliya.
